Q: How to change the style of a radio button with javascript when clicked A: <pre><code>            // get selected radio
            let selectedColor = document.querySelector('input[name=&quot;color&quot;]:checked').value;

            // change background color
            document.body.style.backgroundColor = selectedColor;

</code></pre>

Q: An entire UI shifts upward when keyboard appears in .NET 9 MAUI app A: <p>Add this to MainActivity.cs</p>
<pre><code>protected override void OnCreate(Bundle savedInstanceState)
{
    base.OnCreate(savedInstanceState);

    Window?.SetSoftInputMode(Android.Views.SoftInput.AdjustNothing);
}
</code></pre>
